# Pannable Interactive Tag Cloud â€” Shopify Editions Section Prototype

This is a static web prototype.
It features a **spatially mapped interactive tag cloud**, including:

- Proximity-based micro-interactions (scale, opacity, font colour fade)
- Hover-activated modal interaction cards on desktop
- Tap-activated modals and pannable left-right canvas on mobile
- Fully clickable CTA links inside modal popups
- Desktop-first responsive layout

## Tech Used
- HTML
- CSS (no external dependencies)
- Vanilla JavaScript for interactions
- Hosted on Vercel

## Deployment
1. Upload `index.html` to the repository root
2. Import this repository into Vercel
3. Select **Other / Static** as framework
4. Deploy

